KwaZulu-Natal Legislature in Pietermaritzburg. PIETERMARITZBURG - KwaZulu-Natal Premier Nomusa Dube-Ncube delivers the 2023 State of the Province Address. It is the Dube-Ncube's maiden adress. The speech was delivered at the Oval Cricket Stadium in Pietermaritzburg, comes as KwaZulu-Natal continues to chart the path of economic recovery following the adverse impact of COVID-19, the civil unrest of July 2021 and the flood disasters on the province’s economy. 